longBusinessSummary: Geopulse Exploration, Inc. develops blockchain-powered logistics, financial services, and promotion platform for United States and Canadian cannabis sector. The company has a strategic development partnership with NetCents Technology Inc. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
